    "body": "### Problem\n\n```console\n infocmp tmux-direct | sed -n /colors/p\n            colors#0x1000000, cols#80, it#8, lines#24, pairs#0x10000,\n```\nthe first command output **1677721**, but it should be **16777216** (second command)\n```console\nTERM=tmux-direct nvim -c \":echo &t_Co\"\nTERM=tmux-direct nvim -c \":lua=0x1000000\"\n```\n\n[TCO_BUFFER_SIZE](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/f60f67c2de0f3e03309233e6e247313af8fc4018/src/nvim/option.c#L2996) should be `8 + 1` instead of 8\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nin problem\n\n### Expected behavior\n\noutput `16777216` instead of truncated `1677721`\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.11.4\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nyes, 9.1.1566\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nlinux\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nwezterm\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-direct\n\n### Installation\n\nnixpkgs",
